| R5 | [3-flat-orchestration.mdc](./3-flat-orchestration.mdc) | Use cases and application layer |
| R6 | [3-typed-boundaries.mdc](./3-typed-boundaries.mdc) | Controllers, repositories, external APIs |
| R7 | [3-module-isolation.mdc](./3-module-isolation.mdc) | Imports between modules |

## Decision policy

1. **Pure business logic?** → Rules **R1–R4**, then **R7** for imports.
2. **Nest use case?** → Rule **R5**, then **R6** for DTO validation.
3. **HTTP or DB code?** → Rule **R6**, then **R7** for cross-module access.
4. **Unsure?** → Start with **R4** (pure domain) and **R7** (isolation).

